description: Emerge ETCHGNBW Retractable Universal Notebook ChargerThe ETCHGNBW retractable universal notebook charger by Emerge is a great replacement or upgrade for almost any notebook computer.  Say goodbye to the days of winding or unwinding cables each time you use or pack-up your laptop.  The specially designed charger features retractable cables that can be extended to your desired length and will hide the cords completely when retracted all the way.9-1/2-feet of total expanded lengthThe extra long cable eliminates the need to setup camp next to the nearest outlet.  You’ll be able to comfortably sit in a roomy 9-1/2-foot proximity to the outlet.  Easily expand both the wall-to-converter cable and the converter-to-PC cable to the desired length without the clutter of unwanted cable.Compact – up to 60-percent smallerThe retractable charger occupies very little space in your briefcase or luggage which makes it great for traveling.  Simply retract the cables, place the charger in the included cinch bag and you’re ready to go without any hassle.9 interchangeable adaptersThe retractable charger is compatible with over 7,000 notebook models and 10 major brands including: Dell, Sony VAIO, Samsung, Toshiba, Acer, Winbook, Gateway, Thinkpad, Compaq and HP.  Use it interchangeably with your home and work laptop, or between a family member’s laptop and your own.  The ETCHGNBW is compatible with the following models.
